Distribution . West Atlantic: Belize , Honduras , Nicaragua , Costa Rica , Panama (Bahía Limón / Panama Canal área, west of Colón ), Colombia , Venezuela , Suriname and Brazil from Pará to Santa Catarina (Holthuis 1959; Gore & Shoup 1968 ; Gore 1974;
